CREDITS

This project builds upon the pfQuest framework created by Shagu (Eric Mauser).

Original pfQuest:
- Created by: Shagu (Eric Mauser)
- Repository: https://github.com/shagu/pfQuest
- Core database and rendering engine

Enhanced Features by XiusTV:
- Automated quest capture system with live database injection
- Performance optimizations (~70% CPU reduction)
- Quest capture UI and monitoring tools
- External merger tool for permanent database integration
- Bronzebeard realm-specific extensions
- WotLK 3.3.5 optimizations and enhancements

Database Sources:
- VMaNGOS project - Vanilla quest data
- CMaNGOS project - TBC quest data
- MaNGOS Extras - Translations and additional data
- Community captures - Expanding WotLK database

All quest capture systems, performance optimizations, and realm-specific features
are original work by XiusTV, building on the pfQuest framework by Shagu.

